high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter and take a step to the left.
Wash the plate in the sink and pick it back up and close the tap,
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right.
Put the plate to the right of the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick the plate up from the far left side of the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the plate in the sink, turn the water on, turn the water off, and pick the plate up out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelves at the end of the counter.
Put the plate on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on a shelf.

high_descs: Take the dirty plate off the edge of the table.
Turn to the left and walk across the room to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink and turn the water on, then fill up the sink before turning it off and taking the plate out of the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right.
Put the plate on the second shelf from the bottom.
